OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'beautiful
OL,4,Cspirit' of stabbing victim found in
OL,5,Cgarden
OL,7,FThe family of a 35-year-old man who
OL,8,Fdied after he was found with stab
OL,9,Fwounds in an east London garden have
OL,10,Fpaid tribute to a "beautiful spirit"
OL,11,Fwho brought "love, light and joy" to
OL,12,Fall who knew him.
OL,14,FMark Orabiyi was found in the garden
OL,15,Fof a property in Rayleigh Road,
OL,16,FSilvertown, after police were called
OL,17,Fto reports of a stabbing in nearby
OL,18,FPankhurt Avenue at around 9am on
OL,19,FFriday, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,26,@rD@SOUrD@dO]sD@MOUsD@aO]
