PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1781000202
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'beautiful
OL,4,Cspirit' of stabbing victim found in
OL,5,Cgarden
OL,7,FMr Orabiyi was taken to hospital but
OL,8,Fdied on arrival, despite the efforts
OL,9,Fof paramedics.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Mr Orabiyi's family
OL,12,Fsaid: "Mark was a beloved son,
OL,13,Fbrother, uncle and friend. He brought
OL,14,Flove, light and joy to our family and
OL,15,Fto all who knew him.
OL,17,F"We will always cherish his kindness,
OL,18,Fbeautiful spirit and remarkable
OL,19,Ftalent. His presence touched many
OL,20,Flives and his memory will remain in
OL,21,Four hearts forever.
OL,26,@tD@GOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
