OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'beautiful
OL,4,Cspirit' of stabbing victim found in
OL,5,Cgarden
OL,7,F"May his soul rest in perfect peace."
OL,9,FA second man in his 20s, who also
OL,10,Fsuffered stab wounds, remains in
OL,11,Fhospital, police said.
OL,13,FHis condition is not believed to be
OL,14,Flife-threatening or life-changing.
OL,16,FThe police have launched an
OL,17,Finvestigation and three people have
OL,18,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder,
OL,19,Fthe Met said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@eO]
